[[=]]
**SCP-6858: "The Wolf, Down"**
No bark, no bite.

[[image http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/this-page-intentionally-left-blank/6858.png]]

**[[[http://www.scp-wiki.net/this-page-intentionally-left-blank|More by this author!]]]**
[[/=]]
[[include :scp-wiki:info:end]]

[[f<image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-6858/activewolf.jpg]]

++ ##FF0000|ARTICLE 1964-H-17##
++ **DESIGNATION** -- "Cardinal"

**PRIORITY**
##FF0000|â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…##

**CATEGORY** 
Entity

**GENUS** 
//H. sapiens lupus Nova Gallia//

**STATUS** 
